ISLAMABAD, Feb 24 (APP): Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif on Monday extended his heartfelt congratulations to Friedrich Merz and Germany’s conservative CDU/CSU bloc on their “impressive win” in Germany’s recent election.
“I look forward to working with the new government to further strengthen the Pakistan – Germany partnership,” the prime minister wrote on his official X handle.
